1
00:01:01,520 --> 00:01:02,159
Five Thunders, Five Thunders

2
00:01:02,200 --> 00:01:02,840
Heavenly thunder, follow!

3
00:01:02,880 --> 00:01:03,520
Thunder in my palm

4
00:01:03,520 --> 00:01:04,280
Smiting ghosts, banishing evil

5
00:01:12,760 --> 00:01:13,920
Great General, descend!

6
00:01:20,840 --> 00:01:21,480
You filthy pervert!

7
00:01:21,480 --> 00:01:22,640
Why are you grabbing my chest?

8
00:01:23,159 --> 00:01:23,799
You're a perfectly fine human,

9
00:01:23,799 --> 00:01:24,239
yet you refuse to act like one.

10
00:01:24,239 --> 00:01:25,159
Why pretend to be a ghost?

11
00:01:25,799 --> 00:01:27,719
How do you know I'm human, not a ghost?

12
00:01:29,239 --> 00:01:30,879
I saw you at the execution ground today.

13
00:01:31,640 --> 00:01:32,200
What's going on?

14
00:01:32,799 --> 00:01:33,560
Another execution?

15
00:01:42,480 --> 00:01:43,000
Hey, boss

16
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:44,000
Give me two buns

17
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:45,400
Me too, me too!

18
00:01:45,400 --> 00:01:46,200
Give me two as well

19
00:01:46,200 --> 00:01:47,400
Pay up, pay up!

20
00:01:47,400 --> 00:01:49,239
Don't touch my husband's body!

21
00:01:49,239 --> 00:01:50,480
Stop grabbing!

22
00:01:50,480 --> 00:01:51,079
No!

23
00:01:51,200 --> 00:01:52,159
I'm begging you!

24
00:01:52,159 --> 00:01:53,519
Hurry, hurry, hurry!

25
00:02:02,200 --> 00:02:03,359
Thank you, Benefactor

26
00:02:05,799 --> 00:02:06,719
Get up

27
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:11,719
What's your name?

28
00:02:12,479 --> 00:02:13,599
My name is Ruling

29
00:02:14,879 --> 00:02:17,560
I came to Yinyang Ferry just to scrape by

30
00:02:18,520 --> 00:02:20,280
But I ran into Lord Beile

31
00:02:20,360 --> 00:02:22,039
He tried to force me to be his concubine

32
00:02:22,639 --> 00:02:24,159
My husband argued with him

33
00:02:25,520 --> 00:02:27,439
So he framed him as Revolutionary Party.

34
00:02:27,719 --> 00:02:28,319
And the result...

35
00:02:44,199 --> 00:02:45,039
Why did you

36
00:02:45,199 --> 00:02:46,199
pretend to be a ghost to scare me?

37
00:02:46,800 --> 00:02:48,960
I played ghost to scare him

38
00:02:50,039 --> 00:02:51,680
I knew that after my husband's death

39
00:02:52,479 --> 00:02:54,240
Lord Beile wouldn't let me go

40
00:02:59,159 --> 00:02:59,759
Step aside

41
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:02,560
What are you doing?

42
00:03:09,479 --> 00:03:10,319
I didn't expect

43
00:03:10,800 --> 00:03:12,360
you're a corpse stitcher too

44
00:03:14,039 --> 00:03:15,280
Better to be a streetwalker

45
00:03:15,520 --> 00:03:16,479
than a corpse stitcher

46
00:03:17,280 --> 00:03:18,960
I saw combat in the army

47
00:03:19,639 --> 00:03:20,879
After stitching up so many bodies

48
00:03:21,159 --> 00:03:21,879
you just learn how

49
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:25,919
Dawn's breaking

50
00:03:26,319 --> 00:03:27,759
Hire some people to bury him

51
00:03:30,439 --> 00:03:31,439
Thank you, Benefactor

52
00:03:32,039 --> 00:03:32,879
Up, up, up

53
00:03:33,280 --> 00:03:33,680
Come on

54
00:03:37,879 --> 00:03:38,800
You should leave as soon as possible too

55
00:03:38,800 --> 00:03:39,759
This place is full of trouble

56
00:03:40,840 --> 00:03:42,120
But what about you, Benefactor?

57
00:03:42,680 --> 00:03:44,120
They won't let you go

58
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:53,120
Just hurry up and eat

59
00:03:55,360 --> 00:03:56,560
Got it open

60
00:04:07,560 --> 00:04:09,199
You really are Lao Jiugui

61
00:04:11,919 --> 00:04:12,840
You know me?

62
00:04:13,560 --> 00:04:14,439
In this Yinyang Town

63
00:04:14,439 --> 00:04:15,800
who doesn't know you?

64
00:04:16,160 --> 00:04:17,920
They make you sound legendary

65
00:04:19,519 --> 00:04:20,560
They say you

66
00:04:21,360 --> 00:04:22,839
are the Descent of Zhong Kui

67
00:04:23,360 --> 00:04:24,279
Some others

68
00:04:24,839 --> 00:04:26,680
say you're the King of Hell reborn

69
00:04:36,240 --> 00:04:37,279
Are you disgusted by me?

70
00:04:40,720 --> 00:04:41,480
No

71
00:04:42,040 --> 00:04:42,839
Not at all

72
00:04:45,639 --> 00:04:46,680
Hurry up and eat

73
00:04:46,879 --> 00:04:47,800
After you finish

74
00:04:48,839 --> 00:04:49,800
get to bed early

75
00:04:53,040 --> 00:04:54,319
Where am I supposed to sleep in this room?

76
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:06,160
Did you save me

77
00:05:06,519 --> 00:05:07,720
just to sleep with me?

78
00:05:51,839 --> 00:05:52,399
Who's there?

79
00:06:01,759 --> 00:06:02,560
Who?

80
00:06:09,759 --> 00:06:10,560
Who?

81
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:29,720
What is it?

82
00:06:29,720 --> 00:06:30,160
Master

83
00:06:30,360 --> 00:06:31,560
There's a woman on the roadside

84
00:06:32,399 --> 00:06:33,120
Where?

85
00:06:33,720 --> 00:06:34,519
Right over there

86
00:06:44,319 --> 00:06:46,279
Could you take me home?

87
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:47,680
Hold on

88
00:06:48,759 --> 00:06:49,959
Don't you find it strange?

89
00:06:50,920 --> 00:06:52,120
What's so strange about it?

90
00:06:52,439 --> 00:06:53,600
In the middle of the night

91
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:55,439
why would she be out here?

92
00:06:56,040 --> 00:06:56,879
In the middle of the night

93
00:06:57,040 --> 00:06:58,720
why are we out here ourselves?

94
00:06:59,000 --> 00:06:59,600
We're

95
00:06:59,600 --> 00:07:00,360
heading home

96
00:07:02,120 --> 00:07:03,240
Didn't she just say

97
00:07:03,240 --> 00:07:04,120
she's heading home too?

98
00:07:05,160 --> 00:07:05,759
Good point

99
00:07:07,439 --> 00:07:08,160
Hop in the carriage

100
00:07:08,959 --> 00:07:09,800
Much obliged

101
00:07:23,959 --> 00:07:25,279
What is it now?

102
00:07:25,639 --> 00:07:26,279
Master!

103
00:07:27,560 --> 00:07:28,480
Look over there, Master!

104
00:07:30,040 --> 00:07:31,120
What am I supposed to see?

105
00:07:32,839 --> 00:07:34,040
There was clearly someone

106
00:07:34,040 --> 00:07:35,480
dressed in Qing Dynasty clothes!

107
00:07:36,279 --> 00:07:37,560
What Qing Dynasty person?

108
00:07:37,560 --> 00:07:38,759
It's the Republic era now.

109
00:07:41,160 --> 00:07:41,480
Let's go.

110
00:07:41,839 --> 00:07:42,199
Yah!

111
00:07:43,720 --> 00:07:44,759
It's nothing.

112
00:07:45,040 --> 00:07:45,800
Just now,

113
00:07:46,000 --> 00:07:47,879
the driver was just seeing things.

114
00:08:06,800 --> 00:08:07,360
Yah!

115
00:08:22,759 --> 00:08:24,040
On Yinyang Ridge,

116
00:08:24,160 --> 00:08:25,959
corpses have shown up for days now.

117
00:08:26,319 --> 00:08:27,480
Tell me, what's going on?

118
00:08:28,240 --> 00:08:29,519
We don't know either.

119
00:08:30,319 --> 00:08:31,399
As Neighborhood Chiefs,

120
00:08:31,920 --> 00:08:32,639
something this serious happens

121
00:08:32,639 --> 00:08:33,679
and you say you don't know?

122
00:08:35,159 --> 00:08:36,000
This is a grave matter.

123
00:08:36,360 --> 00:08:37,799
We should report it to the county.

124
00:08:38,440 --> 00:08:38,840
Right.

125
00:08:39,080 --> 00:08:40,000
Report it to the county,

126
00:08:41,039 --> 00:08:42,279
and I'm finished as Mayor.

127
00:08:42,399 --> 00:08:43,879
And you Neighborhood Chiefs can all get lost.

128
00:08:45,320 --> 00:08:45,840
Oh, right, right, right.

129
00:08:46,039 --> 00:08:46,679
Then we'd better

130
00:08:46,879 --> 00:08:47,639
handle it ourselves.

131
00:08:47,639 --> 00:08:48,279
Yes, yes, yes.

132
00:08:52,799 --> 00:08:53,519
Daoist Priest,

133
00:08:53,879 --> 00:08:54,799
about this matter,

134
00:08:54,799 --> 00:08:55,879
do you have any insight?

135
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:01,480
These corpses

136
00:09:02,320 --> 00:09:04,559
were drained of blood.

137
00:09:05,919 --> 00:09:06,679
Therefore,

138
00:09:06,759 --> 00:09:07,639
I conclude

139
00:09:08,039 --> 00:09:10,200
that the Lady Fox Spirit of Yinyang Ridge

140
00:09:11,879 --> 00:09:12,879
has grown wrathful.

141
00:09:13,360 --> 00:09:14,080
The Fox Spirit's wrath?

142
00:09:14,879 --> 00:09:15,960
The Lady Fox Spirit?

143
00:09:18,519 --> 00:09:19,440
These past few days,

144
00:09:20,120 --> 00:09:21,759
didn't someone see the Lady Fox Spirit

145
00:09:21,759 --> 00:09:23,000
take a zombie away?

146
00:09:25,799 --> 00:09:27,080
It's precisely because

147
00:09:27,080 --> 00:09:28,720
the Lady Fox Spirit is enraged

148
00:09:29,519 --> 00:09:31,440
that she has unleashed from the woods

149
00:09:31,600 --> 00:09:32,879
demons and corpse fiends.

150
00:09:33,799 --> 00:09:34,360
Well...

151
00:09:35,159 --> 00:09:35,559
Then...

152
00:09:36,200 --> 00:09:37,440
What do we do then?

153
00:09:51,840 --> 00:09:53,679
By my divination,

154
00:09:55,000 --> 00:09:56,840
prepare young boys and girls.

155
00:09:57,480 --> 00:09:59,440
At midnight three days from now,

156
00:10:00,240 --> 00:10:01,799
offer them to the Lady Fox Spirit.

157
00:10:03,639 --> 00:10:04,720
Otherwise,

158
00:10:05,759 --> 00:10:07,639
your Yinyang Ferry

159
00:10:08,399 --> 00:10:11,519
will never know peace again.

160
00:10:11,960 --> 00:10:12,399
Good.

161
00:10:12,399 --> 00:10:13,399
Now that we know what's going on,

162
00:10:13,600 --> 00:10:14,279
go and get it done.

163
00:10:14,960 --> 00:10:15,279
But...

164
00:10:15,279 --> 00:10:17,279
who would give up their child

165
00:10:17,279 --> 00:10:18,559
to sacrifice to the Lady Fox Spirit?

166
00:10:18,919 --> 00:10:20,240
You really are a fool.

167
00:10:20,639 --> 00:10:22,639
If they won't give a child, make them pay!

168
00:10:22,960 --> 00:10:23,679
Take that money

169
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:25,159
and give it to families with children.

170
00:10:25,399 --> 00:10:26,840
A heavy reward draws brave takers.

171
00:10:26,840 --> 00:10:28,159
Don't you get that?

172
00:10:31,720 --> 00:10:32,960
Brilliant, Mayor!

173
00:10:35,519 --> 00:10:37,159
Let me go! Let me go!

174
00:10:38,799 --> 00:10:39,440
You shut your mouth!

175
00:10:39,440 --> 00:10:39,840
You little brat!

176
00:10:40,919 --> 00:10:42,039
You actually bit me?

177
00:10:42,240 --> 00:10:42,879
Screw you!

178
00:10:45,240 --> 00:10:46,279
It's about time, isn't it?

179
00:10:50,559 --> 00:10:51,440
I'll teach you to bite me!

180
00:10:51,639 --> 00:10:52,679
I'll teach you to bite me!

181
00:10:53,000 --> 00:10:54,080
I'll teach you to bite me!

182
00:10:54,639 --> 00:10:56,399
Mayor, I beg you!

183
00:10:56,840 --> 00:10:58,279
Dongsheng's father died young.

184
00:10:58,440 --> 00:11:00,639
We only have each other to rely on.

185
00:11:00,919 --> 00:11:02,720
I beg you, please spare us!

186
00:11:03,039 --> 00:11:03,639
Dongsheng's mother,

187
00:11:03,919 --> 00:11:05,240
Men and women should not have physical contact.

188
00:11:05,679 --> 00:11:06,679
We can't be doing this.

189
00:11:06,960 --> 00:11:07,799
You already took the money.

190
00:11:08,159 --> 00:11:09,039
You can't go back on it now.

191
00:11:11,039 --> 00:11:11,840
What money?

192
00:11:13,919 --> 00:11:14,600
I completely forgot.

193
00:11:14,600 --> 00:11:15,960
I'll give it back now, right now!

194
00:11:24,120 --> 00:11:25,039
I don't want money

195
00:11:25,039 --> 00:11:26,559
I just want Dongsheng, Mayor.

196
00:11:26,799 --> 00:11:28,120
Don't tell me you took their money too

197
00:11:28,120 --> 00:11:28,559
I'm begging you

198
00:11:29,320 --> 00:11:30,159
If I didn't take the money,

199
00:11:30,320 --> 00:11:31,759
how would I feed my boys at home?

200
00:11:32,799 --> 00:11:33,759
Worthless burden

201
00:11:33,960 --> 00:11:34,679
Once sold, she's sold.

202
00:11:35,320 --> 00:11:36,159
Mayor

203
00:11:36,879 --> 00:11:38,039
The auspicious hour is passing

204
00:11:38,240 --> 00:11:39,559
And she's still wailing here

205
00:11:40,279 --> 00:11:41,759
Lady Fox Spirit

206
00:11:42,240 --> 00:11:43,879
is going to get angry again

207
00:11:44,840 --> 00:11:45,440
Yes, yes, yes

208
00:11:46,320 --> 00:11:47,519
Take the money and go home

209
00:11:47,639 --> 00:11:48,480
I don't want money

210
00:11:48,480 --> 00:11:49,519
I just want Dongsheng

211
00:11:49,519 --> 00:11:50,120
I don't want money

212
00:11:50,120 --> 00:11:51,120
Take the money, hurry up

213
00:11:52,759 --> 00:11:53,960
Why are you talking so much?

214
00:11:54,200 --> 00:11:55,600
You scared the hell out of me!

215
00:11:57,879 --> 00:11:58,360
Drag her away

216
00:12:04,720 --> 00:12:05,519
Look at this

217
00:12:06,399 --> 00:12:07,639
One drama after another

218
00:12:07,639 --> 00:12:08,759
How much time has been wasted?

219
00:12:09,440 --> 00:12:10,360
Hurry up and light the fire

220
00:12:11,559 --> 00:12:12,120
Right away

221
00:12:15,399 --> 00:12:15,879
Who's there?

222
00:12:16,320 --> 00:12:16,960
Who?

223
00:12:18,440 --> 00:12:19,000
Me

224
00:12:19,840 --> 00:12:20,200
Me

225
00:12:23,399 --> 00:12:24,080
You must be

226
00:12:24,399 --> 00:12:26,279
Colonel Commander Lao Jiugui, right?

227
00:12:27,320 --> 00:12:29,080
We've been looking for you all this time

228
00:12:29,279 --> 00:12:29,960
Well, here I am

229
00:12:29,960 --> 00:12:30,679
He's Lao Jiugui

230
00:12:31,440 --> 00:12:31,799
Commander

231
00:12:31,840 --> 00:12:32,679
Hello

232
00:12:32,679 --> 00:12:33,360
Look, when has our Mayor

233
00:12:33,519 --> 00:12:34,480
ever been this polite to anyone?

234
00:12:35,240 --> 00:12:36,600
Our daughter is saved

235
00:12:36,960 --> 00:12:37,559
Mayor

236
00:12:38,000 --> 00:12:39,360
In the middle of the night

237
00:12:39,639 --> 00:12:41,200
coming all the way to Wild Fox Ridge

238
00:12:41,440 --> 00:12:42,240
what are you up to?

239
00:12:43,120 --> 00:12:44,039
We

240
00:12:44,039 --> 00:12:44,799
are of course

241
00:12:45,000 --> 00:12:46,639
making offerings to Lady Fox Spirit

242
00:12:47,200 --> 00:12:49,399
And why make offerings to Lady Fox Spirit?

243
00:12:49,919 --> 00:12:51,159
Lady Fox Spirit

244
00:12:51,919 --> 00:12:52,879
is angry

245
00:12:53,519 --> 00:12:54,559
She's already taken

246
00:12:54,799 --> 00:12:55,840
several lives

247
00:13:01,799 --> 00:13:03,000
You're pinning all this

248
00:13:03,200 --> 00:13:04,879
on Lady Fox Spirit?

249
00:13:06,320 --> 00:13:07,000
Old Commander

250
00:13:07,159 --> 00:13:08,039
For this kind of thing

251
00:13:08,360 --> 00:13:09,200
better to believe it exists

252
00:13:09,559 --> 00:13:10,720
than to deny it, right?

253
00:13:11,120 --> 00:13:12,000
Mayor

254
00:13:12,200 --> 00:13:12,840
If it exists

255
00:13:13,200 --> 00:13:13,919
then it exists

256
00:13:14,840 --> 00:13:15,799
If it doesn't

257
00:13:16,679 --> 00:13:17,679
then it doesn't

258
00:13:17,960 --> 00:13:19,159
Lao Jiugui

259
00:13:19,759 --> 00:13:21,399
How do you prove it doesn't exist?

260
00:13:23,600 --> 00:13:24,559
Old Daoist Priest

261
00:13:25,240 --> 00:13:27,120
How do you prove it does?

262
00:13:42,000 --> 00:13:42,480
Fine

263
00:13:43,759 --> 00:13:45,759
I hear you've also studied

264
00:13:45,759 --> 00:13:46,879
Qimen Dunjia

265
00:13:46,879 --> 00:13:47,919
and the arts of Yin and Yang

266
00:13:49,039 --> 00:13:51,000
If you walk into Wild Fox Ridge

267
00:13:51,000 --> 00:13:52,080
and come back alive

268
00:13:52,200 --> 00:13:52,840
how about this?

269
00:13:55,639 --> 00:13:56,960
I'll tuck my tail

270
00:13:57,639 --> 00:13:58,919
and get out of Yinyang Ferry

271
00:13:59,159 --> 00:14:00,159
A man's word

272
00:14:00,279 --> 00:14:01,279
is his bond

273
00:14:01,480 --> 00:14:02,840
And the money you took from the people?

274
00:14:04,000 --> 00:14:06,159
Naturally, it'll all be returned

275
00:14:06,320 --> 00:14:07,200
And these two children?

276
00:14:07,840 --> 00:14:08,679
They go back to their own homes

277
00:14:08,919 --> 00:14:09,720
back to their own mothers

278
00:14:10,320 --> 00:14:10,879
Good

279
00:14:11,919 --> 00:14:13,120
Within half an hour

280
00:14:14,000 --> 00:14:15,240
if I don't come back out

281
00:14:16,120 --> 00:14:17,559
burn what needs burning

282
00:14:18,639 --> 00:14:19,600
take what needs taking
